 voi odihni pre voi... }{\f121\fs26\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Odih-ni\'fei-v\'e3 \'een Domnul, \'bai la suspinele Dumneavoas\-tr\'e3 El v\'e3 va trimite m\'e2ng\'e2iere.}{
\par }{\fs26\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 E dureros c\'e2nd moare cineva. }{\f121\fs26\lang1048\langfe1033\langnp1048 Iat\'e3, \'bai Dum\-neavoastr\'e3 vesti\'fei c\'e3 v-a murit so\'feia, vr\'e2nd s\'e3 spune\'fei prin asta c\'e3 s-a \'eent\'e2
